  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't deliver enough chickens or pork or whatever, you name it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And another barrack was there, I don't know what, but it just called it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was by the gypsies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had about 200 gypsies incarcerated there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So these were the four barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, the next morning, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we had to-- had to get up early in the morning, and they marched us to the rail, to that sand pit, to board flat bed cars that took us to Malkinia and Ostrow Mazowiecka, respectively, to work on the railroad, to unload coals, to-- to-- to-- to-- to align railroad ties.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To Malkinia, it would be about 45 minutes, to Ostrow Mazowiecka would be about two hours from-- from-- from the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I did that, along with another group, for about three weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And every day, so and so many hundred went, and so many bodies we brought back, and they immediately-- either they were shot there during work, or they were beaten to death, or they just died from natural causes.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that went on for about three weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I would estimate it must have been about [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] August [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 10, or 12, or 15, or maybe a little earlier.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1943, we came back from one of our [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] daily journeys to-- I think that day we went Ostrow Mazowiecka to [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as mentioned before, before you get to Treblinka I, you have to pass Treblinka II, which was the extermination camp, which incidentally had their own group of workers that were processing their daily chores.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
